      "rationale": "F1717 fixture geometry (35 mm offset, UHMWPE blocks) replicated in FEA. Load application point and constraint nodes matched to physical fixture. Material inputs derived from measured coupon data. Equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis showing <3% QoI sensitivity to input perturbations within measurement uncertainty."
